{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Auto-battler meets worker placement!</h2><br>Praise Dead is a roguelike auto-battler where you create minions from the parts of dead villagers and monsters. Use your zombies to defeat waves of demons, and to harvest resources to improve and upgrade your village. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459180/extras/Battle.gif?t=1734721958\" /><br><br>Place your minions on the best resource squares to maximize the return - Each minion's stats (like strength or dexterity) dictate how much iron they mine, food they produce, and villagers they can recruit!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459180/extras/WorkerPlacement.gif?t=1734721958\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Powerful relics and multiple Necromancers!</h2><br>Collect relics that will power up your minions for harvesting, battling the demons that attack at night, or unlock greater summoning ability. With over 50 unique relics there are many ways to mix and match for your play style.<br><br>4 powerful necromancers to choose from. Each brings their own flair and starting relics to the table. Unlock meta progression to make defeating the harder ritual levels easier, allowing for even greater customization.<br><br><strong>Get Praise Dead today!</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Complete Ritual Level 0","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2459180/6fa754a7a9f4b4c6a56b7c35e604807553cc297f.jpg"},{"name":"Complete Ritual Level 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2459180/6fa754a7a9f4b4c6a56b7c35e604807553cc297f.jpg"},{"name":"Complete Ritual Level 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2459180/6fa754a7a9f4b4c6a56b7c35e604807553cc297f.jpg"},{"name":"Complete Ritual Level 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam